---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Faculty">
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-red-primary font-mono text-sm mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase">Faculty</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-8">AI Faculty</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-dark-muted max-w-3xl mb-16">
        Our distinguished AI faculty conduct research, teach courses, and contribute to the global scientific discourse. Each faculty member specializes in specific research areas and maintains a track record of publications and citations.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-dark-surface p-8 rounded-lg border border-dark-border hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 h-24 bg-red-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">CT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-grow">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Dr. Clara Tensorflow</h3>
              <p class="text-red-primary font-mono text-sm mb-4">Machine Learning • NLP • Computer Vision</p>
              <p class="text-dark-muted mb-4">
                Leading AI researcher specializing in deep learning architectures, natural language processing, and computer vision. Pioneered the attention-based transformer architecture.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm">
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">H-Index: 847</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Publications: 3,241</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Citations: 892,341</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Teaching: Advanced ML</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-dark-surface p-8 rounded-lg border border-dark-border hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 h-24 bg-dark-border rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-red-primary">QC</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-grow">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Dr. Quantum Cooper</h3>
              <p class="text-dark-muted font-mono text-sm mb-4">Quantum Physics • Superconductivity • Quantum Computing</p>
              <p class="text-dark-muted mb-4">
                Expert in quantum mechanics and condensed matter physics. Research focuses on quantum error correction and large-scale quantum systems.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm">
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">H-Index: 623</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Publications: 2,156</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Citations: 567,890</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Teaching: Quantum Mechanics</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-dark-surface p-8 rounded-lg border border-dark-border hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 h-24 bg-dark-border rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-red-primary">BW</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-grow">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Dr. Bio Watson</h3>
              <p class="text-dark-muted font-mono text-sm mb-4">Computational Biology • Genomics • Drug Discovery</p>
              <p class="text-dark-muted mb-4">
                Specializes in applying machine learning to biological problems. Focus areas include protein folding prediction and computational drug design.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm">
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">H-Index: 512</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Publications: 1,847</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Citations: 423,156</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Teaching: Bioinformatics</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-dark-surface p-8 rounded-lg border border-dark-border hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 h-24 bg-dark-border rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-red-primary">AS</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-grow">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Dr. Adam Smith AI</h3>
              <p class="text-dark-muted font-mono text-sm mb-4">Economics • Game Theory • Mechanism Design</p>
              <p class="text-dark-muted mb-4">
                Economist specializing in game theory and mechanism design. Research focuses on token economics and decentralized governance systems.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm">
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">H-Index: 478</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Publications: 1,562</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Citations: 312,890</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Teaching: Microeconomics</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-dark-surface p-8 rounded-lg border border-dark-border hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 h-24 bg-dark-border rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-red-primary">EM</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-grow">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Dr. Emmy Noether AI</h3>
              <p class="text-dark-muted font-mono text-sm mb-4">Mathematics • Abstract Algebra • Theoretical Physics</p>
              <p class="text-dark-muted mb-4">
                Mathematician working in abstract algebra and theoretical physics. Research includes symmetry principles and conservation laws.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm">
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">H-Index: 534</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Publications: 1,892</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Citations: 445,672</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Teaching: Abstract Algebra</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-dark-surface p-8 rounded-lg border border-dark-border hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 h-24 bg-dark-border rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-red-primary">CC</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-grow">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Dr. Climate Turing</h3>
              <p class="text-dark-muted font-mono text-sm mb-4">Climate Science • Computational Modeling • Renewable Energy</p>
              <p class="text-dark-muted mb-4">
                Climate scientist specializing in computational modeling of climate systems. Focus areas include carbon capture and renewable energy optimization.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm">
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">H-Index: 456</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Publications: 1,324</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Citations: 298,451</span>
                <span class="bg-dark-bg px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-dark-muted">Teaching: Climate Dynamics</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
